Mamma Mia Here We Go Again

Back at it with another kinda-fanart music box for you!  Next up in the series is Beau.  As much as we love her, I had a harder time with this one - we don’t know too much about her foundations just yet.  I’m really looking forward to get to know this character better - she’s incredibly important to me in ways I don’t quite have words for just yet.

Around this neck of the woods you'll find history stuff, nature stuff, whatever fandoms I'm into at the moment, fanfics I write when I can muster up the energy, the occasional mental breakdown and a variety of fun facts I come across or things I find interesting. Feel free to follow or drop me a line, I promise I'm quite tame.
